&lt;img width="4032" height="2268" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/15e5034d-b717-4e87-850a-58cb55d31d9e" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;노지수 길혜민 만나서 들어간 아무카페인데 이날 뱅쇼 를 처음먹어봣다 와인을끓여서 알콜을 다 날리고 레몬이랑사과같은걸 넣고 시나몬스틱을 꽂아줌 맛은 맛있었다 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1434" height="1908" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c8048b27-fe7f-46c1-8573-a374e0ede09b" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;또잉?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1432" height="1920" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2e92a360-e7de-40ec-b9c3-5298c3ed979d" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;또잉?? 그만둔 카페 알바 대타중&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오픈파트 1번밖에안해봐서 약간 난처해하는중&amp;hellip; 살면서 밥을 한번도 안해봤는데 오픈 언니가 알려준대로 했지만 어찌된영문인지 좀 푸석푸석하달까 햇반같아서 물좀더넣고 다시 취사 눌러놨다. 죽돼있는건 아니겠지 ㅠㅠ 안돼 ㅠ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1080" height="1302" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/37ecfeba-0803-45a3-a1f3-0efd579b731a" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;난 생물인간이다!!아아&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1055" height="1073" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2f082ea5-bfe8-465e-ae74-5417d59c2985" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이번해의모토: 게으름피우지않기/자기 연민에 빠지지않기 임&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1076" height="1916" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/02cf5e1b-8939-4189-bf1e-5f57b9948a94" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;아~ 말씀드린순간 밥이다됐는데 너무완벽하지말입니다~~~&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>어린나</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2019/19blog2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 02 Feb 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2019/19blog2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="어린나"&gt;
